snippet.title: Justin Bieber, Jennifer Lopez, Cardi B & Rihanna #StandWithKeaton
snippet.description:
Some big names in Hollywood are standing with Keaton, a middle-schooler whose heartbreaking video describing the bullying he’s experienced has gone viral. There are so many classes out there for kids, but what about one that teaches them to be kind to one another? Plus, Wish.com is slammed for its ad showing thin models wearing plus-size tights. We show what a real pair of plus-size hosiery looks like!
